FBIS4-995 "drafr075_d_94012" FBIS-AFR-94-075 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Swaziland Defense Force: No Afrikaner Army Training in North Defense Force: No Afrikaner Army Training in North MB1904103094 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0500 GMT 19 Apr 94 MB1904103094 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network English BFN [Text] Swaziland's Defense Force says it knows nothing about members of the Afrikaner Volksfront [National Front] apparently being trained in the north of the territory. This follows allegations by a Swazi chief that Volksfront members were receiving training in the area. The deputy commissioner of the Swazi police, Mr. Esau Dube, said that an investigation in this regard had proved fruitless.
